---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tech Tutoring | Jake Fixes Tech — Littleton, NH"
description="One-on-one tech tutoring in person or remote. Learn at your own pace with patient, friendly help. $50/hr, 30 minute minimum. Serving Littleton NH and the North Country.">

  <!-- Header Banner -->
  <section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;background-color:rgb(30,64,175);">
    <img src="/hero.jpg" alt="Professional tech workspace with dual monitors" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;z-index:0;" />
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(30,64,175,0.88),rgba(37,99,235,0.88));z-index:1;"></div>
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#93c5fd;">
        <a href="/services" style="color:#93c5fd;text-decoration:none;" aria-label="Back to all services">← Services</a>
      </p>
      <h1 style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:white;line-height:1.2;">Tech Tutoring</h1>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;color:#bfdbfe;line-height:1.75;font-size:1.1rem;max-width:42rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        Patient, one-on-one tech help at your pace. In person or remote. No judgment, no rushing — just clear, friendly explanations that actually make sense.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;">
        <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:white;color:#1e40af;font-weight:700;padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;">
          Book a Session
          <svg style="height:1rem;width:1rem;" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white;font-weight:600;padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
          View Pricing
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Info Bar -->
  <section style="background:#1e40af;padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:2rem;text-align:center;">
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:white;">$50/hr</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#bfdbfe;font-weight:600;">30 Minute Minimum</div>
      </div>
      <div style="width:1px;height:2.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);flex-shrink:0;"></div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:white;">In Person or Remote</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#bfdbfe;font-weight:600;">Your Choice</div>
      </div>
      <div style="width:1px;height:2.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);flex-shrink:0;"></div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:white;">Ages 18+</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.8rem;color:#bfdbfe;font-weight:600;">Any Skill Level Welcome</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Is This -->
  <section style="background:#f8fafc;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">How It Works</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">Tech Help on Your Terms</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.75rem;line-height:1.75;">Tech tutoring is one-on-one time with me focused entirely on what you want to learn or understand better. There's no set curriculum and no pressure to keep up. We go at whatever pace works for you, cover whatever topics matter to you, and you ask as many questions as you want. Sessions can be in person in Littleton or remote via video call from wherever you are.</p>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.75rem;line-height:1.75;">This is computer and technology tutoring based on my background as a computer technician. I cover how technology works, how to use it safely, how to maintain it, and how to get more out of the devices and software you already have.</p>
      </div>

      <div id="topics-grid">

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #2563eb;">
          <div class="topic-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Staying Safe Online</h3>
          <p>How to spot phishing emails, avoid scams, browse safely, and protect your personal information. One of the most valuable things anyone can learn.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #15803d;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#15803d;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><ellipse cx="12" cy="12" rx="10" ry="3"/><path d="M2 12c0 1.66 4.48 3 10 3s10-1.34 10-3"/><path d="M2 12v6c0 1.66 4.48 3 10 3s10-1.34 10-3v-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Backups & Data Protection</h3>
          <p>Learn how to set up and manage your own backups so you never lose important files. Covers Time Machine, Windows Backup, external drives, and cloud options.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #7c3aed;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#ede9fe;color:#7c3aed;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Understanding Your Computer</h3>
          <p>What the different parts do, how to keep things running well, what to do when something goes wrong, and when it's worth calling for help vs. handling it yourself.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #c2410c;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#ffedd5;color:#c2410c;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Email & Communication</h3>
          <p>Setting up and managing email accounts, organizing your inbox, understanding spam filters, and using communication tools confidently.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #0369a1;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#e0f2fe;color:#0369a1;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Devices & Setup</h3>
          <p>Getting a new device set up the right way, transferring your data, connecting to WiFi, syncing accounts, and understanding the settings that matter.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #b45309;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#fef3c7;color:#b45309;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>DIY Maintenance</h3>
          <p>Want to run your own malware scans, manage your startup programs, or keep your machine clean and fast yourself? I can walk you through exactly what I do and why.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #15803d;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#15803d;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cloud Services</h3>
          <p>Understanding and using iCloud, Google Drive, OneDrive and other cloud storage tools. Getting them set up, organized, and actually working for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #6d28d9;">
          <div class="topic-icon" style="background:#ede9fe;color:#6d28d9;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Browsers & the Web</h3>
          <p>How to use your browser effectively, manage extensions, clear cache, use bookmarks, and understand what's happening when something goes wrong.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="topic-card" style="border-top:3px solid #2563eb;">
          <div class="topic-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M8 9a4 4 0 1 1 4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Anything Else Tech Related</h3>
          <p>If it involves a computer, phone, tablet, router, smart TV, or any other technology and you want to understand it better — ask. Chances are I can help.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- In Person vs Remote -->
  <section style="background:white;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Session Options</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">In Person or Remote, Your Call</h2>
      </div>
      <div id="session-grid">
        <div class="session-card" style="border:2px solid #2563eb;">
          <div class="session-icon" style="background:#dbeafe;color:#2563eb;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#1e40af;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">In Person</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">I come to you for on-site sessions in the Littleton area. Great if you want hands-on help with your actual setup at home or in your office.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="session-card" style="border:2px solid #15803d;">
          <div class="session-icon" style="background:#dcfce7;color:#15803d;" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#166534;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Remote via Video Call</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">Can't make it in? No problem. Remote sessions work great for most tutoring topics. We connect over <strong>Google Meet</strong> or <strong>Zoom</strong> — I send you a link, no account needed on your end — and I walk you through everything on screen. Need more than tutoring? <a href="/services/remote-support" style="color:#15803d;font-weight:600;">Remote Support</a> is also available.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af,#2563eb);padding:4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:40rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin-bottom:1rem;">Ready to Learn?</h2>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2rem;">No question is too basic and no topic is off limits. Reach out and let me know what you want to learn and we'll set up a session that works for you.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:1rem;">
        <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:white;color:#2563eb;font-weight:700;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;">
          <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          Book a Session
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+18022341552" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);color:white;font-weight:600;padding:0.875rem 2rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-size:1rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">
          <svg style="height:1.25rem;width:1.25rem;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.28h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.96a16 16 0 0 0 6.29 6.29l.54-.54a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21.28 17z"/></svg>
          (802) 234-1552
        </a>
      </div>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <a href="/services" style="color:#bfdbfe;text-decoration:underline;" aria-label="Back to all services">← Back to All Services</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  #topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .topic-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .topic-icon {
    display: flex;
    height: 3rem;
    width: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    background-color: #dbeafe;
    color: #2563eb;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .topic-icon svg {
    height: 1.5rem;
    width: 1.5rem;
  }

  .topic-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .topic-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  #session-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .session-card {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .session-icon {
    display: flex;
    height: 3rem;
    width: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .session-icon svg {
    height: 1.5rem;
    width: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #topics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    #session-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
    #topics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>